Industry body Consulting Engineers South Africa (CESA) on Tuesday inaugurated its new president Sugen Pillay for the next two years. He succeeds Neresh Pather. Pillay serves as MD of Zitholele Consulting and has more than 20 years’ experience in the design and implementation of projects that cover most facets of civil engineering. CESA said its theme for 2020 is “A Time for Reflection, Renewal and Regeneration”.